\c 148 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 148\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Waaqnii Fi Lafti Jajuu Waaqayyootti Waamamuu
\m \bd 1\bd* Waaqayyoon jajadhaa! Bantiiwwan waaqaa keessaa Waaqayyoon jajadhaa, ol gubbaa sanatti isa jajadhaa.
\m \bd 2\bd* Ergamoonni isaa warri waaqa irraa hundinuu isa jajadhaa; macci isaa hundinuus isa jajadhaa!
\m \bd 3\bd* Biiftuu fi ji'i isa jajadhaa, urjoonni calaqqiftanis isa jajadhaa.
\m \bd 4\bd* Bantiiwwan waaqaa warri ol fagoon, isinis bishaanonni bantiiwwan waaqaa irra jirtan, isa jajadhaa!
\m \bd 5\bd* Inni abboomnaan waan uumamaniif, isaan maqaa Waaqayyoo haa jajatan.
\m \bd 6\bd* Inni yeroo hundumaaf baruma baraan cimsee isaan dhaabe, seerrata isaan irra darbuu hin dandeenyes isaaniif in kenne.
\m \bd 7\bd* Isin bineensonni akka jawwee galaanatti galtan, tuujjubni galaanaas, lafaa Waaqayyoon jajadhaa.
\m \bd 8\bd* Isin ibiddii fi qorri, cabbiinii fi hurriin, bubbeen qilleensaa inni abboommii isaa raawwatu.
\m \bd 9\bd* Tulloonni gaaronnis hundinuu, mukkeetiin ija godhatan, gaattiraanis hundinuu, \bd 10\bd* bineensonni, horiin qe'ees hundinuu, warri lafa irra munyuuqan, warri baalleedhaan ka'anis,
\m \bd 11\bd* mootonni lafaa, sabnis hundinuu, gurguddoonni, warri biyya seerratanis hundinuu, \bd 12\bd* dargaggoonni, durboonnis akkasuma, jaarsoliinis ijoollee wajjin, 
\m \bd 13\bd* hundumti isaanii maqaa Waaqayyoo haa jajatan! Maqaan isaa kophaan ol ka'ee waan beekameef, surraan isaa lafaa fi bantii waaqaa gararraa dha.
\m \bd 14\bd* Jajuu ijoollee Israa'el, warra isatti dhi'aatanii, isaaf of kennan hundumaaf, inni gaanfa mataa saba isaa ol qabeera.Waaqayyoon jajadhaa!
